com.valentine.esp.utilities
Class CustomSweepChecker

java.lang.Object
  com.valentine.esp.utilities.CustomSweepChecker

public class CustomSweepChecker
extends Object

Utility class to check to make sure that the custom sweeps passed into it are valid. After calling checkSweeps, two ArrayLists can be gotten out of the object. The first is the adjusted sweeps so that the list of custom sweeps is now valid. And secondly, a numerical list of input sweeps that were invalid.
